message.body: Tess! Are you back? I need a massage!
Lindsey! I am back! I can give you a massage soon! Tomorrow?
Also, can we have a pie making hang out soon? :)
Tomorrow is great!!! Anytime works for me. Yes do you want to bake apple pies this weekend?
This weekend is busy for me! :( unless we do it earlier...like after your massage tomorrow?
Or next week would work for me!
Yeah let's do it tmw if you are up for it! I have all the ingredience except we will need more apples.
Cool! That sounds great! Wanna come over at like 1 for your massage and then we can get apples and make pies?
I'm not gonna tell Julian...I want to surprise him! He's gonna be so happy I made a pie :)
He's is gonna be soooo happy. Do you want to try another pie or is apple Good?
You have a free massage coming to you! You never cashed in your 30th bday massage! :)
I'm cool with apple! Whatever you want to make. You're the pie wizard!
Free massage?!? Agh! Well you gonna get a big tip! I'm running to trader joes today I'll pick up some extra apples since I'm headed there. This is gonna be fun!
I'm on my period I have the worst cramps
Oh no :( I hate that. I just finished mine.
Take it easy today! I'll see you at 1 tomorrow! :)
